 The bots dodged the fire. Gabriel took a shot to the leg. It was minor 
damage nothing serious. He dove down and pulled out another bomb. He inhanced 
its power and planted it on the bot's back while savior distracted him with 
fire energy blast. He pressed the button. He was too close so he would gain 
damage from the explosion. He heard the bomb and was tossed to the tree and  
he struggled to get up.
